com.interpss.core.net.nb

Interface NBEquipConnection

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NBEquipConnectionImpl

    public interface NBEquipConnection
extends NameTag
    A representation of the model object 'NB Equip Connection'. Node-breaker model equipment connection class

    The following features are supported:

    • Substation
    • Bn Node
    • Equip Type
    • Equip
    • From Bus
    • To Bus
    • Tert Bus
    See Also:
    NBModelPackage.getNBEquipConnection()
